---
import MainGridLayout from '@layouts/MainGridLayout.astro';
---

<MainGridLayout title="赞助支持" description="感谢您的支持">
  <div class="flex w-full rounded-[var(--radius-large)] overflow-hidden relative mb-4">
    <div class="card-base z-10 px-6 md:px-9 pt-6 pb-4 relative w-full">
      <div class="relative onload-animation">
        <div
          data-pagefind-body
          data-pagefind-weight="10"
          data-pagefind-meta="title"
          class="transition w-full block font-bold mb-3
          text-3xl md:text-[2.25rem]/[2.75rem]
          text-black/90 dark:text-white/90
          md:before:w-1 before:h-5 before:rounded-md before:bg-[var(--primary)]
          before:absolute before:top-[0.75rem] before:left-[-1.125rem]"
        >
          赞助支持
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="onload-animation">
        <p class="mb-6 text-black/75 dark:text-white/75">
          如果您觉得我的内容对您有帮助，欢迎通过微信赞赏码进行赞助支持。
        </p>

        <div class="donate-content flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="qr-code-section mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-black/90 dark:text-white/90">微信赞赏码</h2>
            <img src="/wx.jpg" alt="微信赞赏码" class="qr-code max-w-[300px] h-auto border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-xl p-4 shadow-lg" />
            <p class="mt-4 text-center text-black/75 dark:text-white/75">扫描上方二维码，通过微信进行赞助</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="donate-message bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/10 p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-green-500">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black/90 dark:text-white/90">感谢您的支持</h3>
            <p class="text-black/75 dark:text-white/75">您的赞助将帮助我持续创作优质内容，感谢您的鼓励与支持！</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainGridLayout>